QuestData.Title: Olemba Seeds
QuestData.Description: Aren't the trees in the forest beautiful? I've often wondered if they would survive on Azeroth.$B$BI'm hesitant to send back seedlings, though. It's a rough trip and they're much harder to transport than something like a sack of seeds. The seeds are stored in tough cones that fall from the tree's branches once they've reached maturity.$B$BIf you come upon some of those cones in your travels, would you mind bringing some of the seeds back to me?
QuestData.LogDescription: Gather 30 Olemba Seeds and return them to Ros'eleth in the Allerian Stronghold.
QuestData.CompletionText: I've started a seed collection, but I'm going to need some help before I have enough to send back to the park in Stormwind.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you for bringing these seeds. I've almost got enough to send back the first batch!
